title: Terrorist Maulana Masood Azhar, head of Pakistan-backed Jaish-e-Mohammad, dead
content: Jaish-e-Mohammad Chief Maulana Masood Azhar is reportedly dead. Sources said that Azhar died on March 2 at a military hospital in Pakistan's Rawalpindi.
